response.original_title: Keith Urban - Live at iTunes Festival - SXSW
response.overview: Event captures the dynamic performance of the acclaimed country artist at one of the industry's most high-profile events. Recorded during the South by Southwest (SXSW) festival, this concert showcases Keith Urban's exceptional guitar skills, charismatic stage presence, and a setlist brimming with his biggest hits. With a mix of energetic tracks and heartfelt ballads, Urban delivers a memorable live experience that highlights his versatility and deep connection with his audience. The performance is a testament to Urban's status as a leading figure in country music, blending infectious rhythms with intimate moments that resonate with fans old and new.
response.title: Keith Urban - Live at iTunes Festival - SXSW
